name: Super Nibbler eXtra
overview: A Worm\Snake game developed by Mehmet Ali Sahin of Backyard Brothers. It has improved graphics and lots of fun extras. A level editor was available for registered users. There are over 100 levels spread over 25 worlds. And all has its own theme/graphics. Fun Pac-Man and Lemmings animations, the powerups and that you receive a password when you have completed a world.
